                },
                {
                    "id" : "rebellose-4" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Prisoner",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "I see... Unfortunately I couldn't reach out to many of the city folk.",
                    "nextId": "rebellose-5"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "rebellose-5" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Rebel",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "I'm not sure we'll be able to survive without their support...",
                    "nextId": "rebellose-7"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "rebellose-7" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Rebel",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "But could you bring the maps and documents?",
                    "nextId": "rebellose-8"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "rebellose-8" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Rebel",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "With them we might be able to steer some of the king's supporters.",
                    "nextId": "rebellose-9"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "rebellose-9" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Prisoner",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "Yes indeed, here is everything I could get.",
                    "nextId": "rebellose-10"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "rebellose-10" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Rebel",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "We thank your effort. I hope we can change the tide of the rebellion..."
                }
            ]
        }
